Finding Aid for Civic Searchlight records, 1913-1995


Finding aid created by: Finding aid prepared by Justin Lee Tyler
Date: Feb. 17, 2010

Revision history:

Title: Civic Searchlight records
Dates: 1913-1995
Quantity: 109.0 linear ft.
General Physical Description note (216 boxes, 1 volume)
Abstract Profiles of candidates from Wayne, Oakland and Macomb Counties. Also includes papers for affiliate organizations of Civic, Inc., Oakland Citizens league and Macomb County Division.
Language:
Repository: Detroit Public Library. Burton Historical Collection.

Other Finding Aids note

Finding aid and white index cards available in the Burton Historical Collection and on the World Wide Web.

Restrictions

Conditions Governing Access note: This collection is open for research use.

Series I : Amendments
General note
